Two Lovers;;59;;82;;R;;Following a broken engagement, sometime photographer Leonard Kraditor (Joaquin Phoenix) moves in with his parents in Brighton Beach. He soon becomes involved with Sandra (Vinessa Shaw), an honest and sensible young woman. They appear to be a perfect match, then Michelle (Gwyneth Paltrow) enters the picture. Beautiful but manipulative, she wraps him around her finger, even though she has a rich, married boyfriend.;;Romance,Drama;;James Gray;;2008;;Joaquin Phoenix,Gwyneth Paltrow,Vinessa Shaw,Isabella Rossellini,Elias Koteas,Moni Monoshov,Julie Budd,Bob Ari;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/two_lovers